11 October 2019- Jaco Verwey from The Golden Triangle Chamber of Commerce and eNCA Reporter Tshego Moagi react to the smell while on the Vaal Dam at the Rietspruit weir where sewage is flowing into the water. 11 October 2019 - Tharina Human, the teacher accused of organising the kidnapping of Amy'Leigh de Jager, was denied bail. 11 October 2019 - Refugees sit outside the UN's offices in Cape Town on 11 October 2019 demanding to be sent home. 11 October 2019 - A patient undergoes surgery at the Envision Centre for Sight to have cataracts removed.